'''Faṭima Mrnisi''' (1940 - 2015) tga yat tamgayt [[Lmɣrib|tamɣribit]] ar tara f tasnamunt d timɣarin.<ref>https://archive.org/details/beyondveilmalefe0000mern</ref>

== Tudrt nns ==
Tlul ɣ 27 Ctmbr 1940 ɣ [[Fas]] gr mnaw n tmɣarin li illan dar jdas. Tɣra dar [[Fransa|ifransiyn]] ayliɣ umzn Lmɣrib.

Tda s Fransa ɣ 1957 afad ataqra tasrtit ɣ Sorbonne d ɣin nit aɣ tga tadukturt.

Ayliɣ turri s Lmɣrib ar tsaqra tasnamunt ɣ taɣiwant n tskla zɣ 1947 ar 1981.

== Idlisn nns ==
Tura mnnaw idlisn f tasnamunt d timɣarin zund

* 1975: ''Beyond the Veil''
* 1983: ''Le Maroc raconté par ses femmes''.
* 1984: ''L’amour dans les pays musulmans''
* 1985: ''Femmes du Gharb''
* 1987: ''Le harem politique – Le Prophète et les femmes''
* 1993: ''Women’s Rebellion and Islamic Memory''
* 1994: ''The Harem Within''
* 2001: ''Scheherazade Goes West''
* 2002: ''Islam and Democracy: Fear of the Modern World''
* 2009: ''Les Femmes Du Maroc''

